<a href="/akira/dtd/3155-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3155">Implement a solid Government brand architecture that's build with strong brand design.&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/4808-4049">Sam Mehrani</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">6 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
